DESCRIPTION:TechTO\n**🎟️ This is a ticketed event. Secure your spot v
 ia our Luma page before you RSVP here.**\n**[https://luma.com/together-tor
 onto-may-4-2026 ](https://luma.com/together-toronto-may-4-2026 )**\n\n**
 ‼️ A valid ticket is required for entry.**\n\n***\n\n**Together Toront
 o** is where the city's tech community comes together for a night of real 
 stories\, genuine connection\, and the kind of conversations that actually
  move the needle.\nNo polished pitches. No surface-level panels. Just foun
 ders getting honest about what it truly takes to launch\, scale\, and grow
  a company in Toronto's fast-moving tech scene - the bold bets\, the unexp
 ected setbacks\, and the creative pivots that made all the difference.\n\n
 **What to expect:**\n🎤 **Founder talks** \\- Short\\\, punchy\\\, and p
 acked with real lessons from builders who've been in the trenches\n💬 **
 Fireside conversations** \\- Deeper dives into the journeys that rarely ge
 t shared on a stage\n🤝 **Open networking** \\- Before\\\, between\\\, a
 nd after the program\\. This is a room full of people worth knowing\\.\n\n
 ***\n\nWhether you're building your first product\, scaling a team\, or ju
 st genuinely curious about how the best Canadian companies get built - you
  belong here.\nCome ready to learn\, connect\, and be part of something bi
 gger than yourself.\n\n**👉 Tickets are available on our Luma page: [htt
 ps://luma.com/together-toronto-may-4-2026](https://luma.com/together-toron
 to-may-4-2026)**\n\n*RSVP here on Meetup after securing your ticket.*
